sentence: what is the first class fare from indianapolis to orlando
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  '"'||v1.fare_basis_code||'"', '"'||v1.class_type||'"',
 '"'||v2.fare_id||'"', '"'||v3.flight_id||'"', '"'||v4.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v5.city_code||'"', '"'||v5.city_name||'"',
 '"'||v6.airport_code||'"', '"'||v7.city_code||'"',
 '"'||v7.city_name||'"' FROM fare v0, fare_basis v1, flight_fare v2,
 flight v3, airport_service v4, city v5, airport_service v6,
 city v7 
WHERE (((v0.fare_basis_code = ANY v1.fare_basis_code) 
AND (v1.class_type = 'FIRST')) AND ((v0.fare_id = ANY v2.fare_id) 
AND ((v2.flight_id = ANY v3.flight_id) 
AND (((v3.from_airport = ANY v4.airport_code) AND ((v4.city_code = ANY v5.city_code) 
AND (v5.city_name = 'INDIANAPOLIS'))) 
AND ((v3.to_airport = ANY v6.airport_code) AND ((v6.city_code = ANY v7.city_code) 
AND (v7.city_name = 'ORLANDO')))))));

FARE_ID IN ( SELECT FLIGHT_FARE . FARE_ID FROM FLIGHT_FARE WHERE FLIGHT_FARE . FLIGHT_ID IN ( SELECT FLIGHT . FLIGHT_ID FROM FLIGHT WHERE ( FLIGHT . FROM_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' INDIANAPOLIS ' ) ) AND FLIGHT . TO_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' ORLANDO ' ) ) ) ) ) ) ) ;
